event handling
addActionNamed: aSymbol 
	"This is a little questionable, but since it is only called from the UI, and the only manually editable children of an action are rules, we can leave out the type of the new child in this method name." 
	| nodeClass |
	nodeClass := self baseNodeClass.
	^ GenericActions
		label: 'add ' , aSymbol asString , ' ', nodeClass label
		receiver: nodeClass
		selector: #addNodesAction:
		arguments: {self}